Create bottom-left chart (Active Students By Month) 15

Select (Line and Clustered Column Chart)  from visualization.

  • Drag and drop the visual to the canvas area .
  • Align the size and add the title for the visual as below .
  • Select Year Month Name ,Year and Quarter from the Calendar Table  and insert it in to Shared Axis .


  • Drag the Correct Measures from the Tier II CAP Table and place it on The correct place as shown below on the gif.


FORMATING FOR THE Visual

  • Width : 531
  • Height : 297
  • Title Font Color : Black
  • Title Background Color : #85ACC6
  • Text Size : 20 pt
  • Font Family : Segoe UI Bold
  • Alignment : Center


Data Color's 

  • % MOM Total Active     : #AC95DA
  • Alumni                                    :  #57ACC1
  • CAP                                          :  #7B876E
